title: Big Steak Omelette
description: Tender and tasty strips of steak, hash browns, fresh green peppers, onions, mushrooms, tomatoes and Cheddar cheese. Enjoy it with salsa on the side.

title: Country Omelette
description: Our delicious blend of ham, cheese, fresh onions and hash browns is topped off just right — with a dollop of sour cream.

title: SIMPLE & FIT Vegetable Omelette
description: Big on flavor, not on calories, and filled with fresh spinach, mushrooms, onions and Swiss cheese, then topped with diced tomatoes. Comes with a side of seasonal mixed fruit. Just 330 calories.

title: Original French Toast
description: You’ll enjoy this IHOP® classic—six fluffy triangle-shaped slices topped with whipped butter and sprinkled with powdered sugar.

title: Strawberry Banana French Toast
description: Enjoy six French toast triangles, topped with cool strawberries, fresh banana slices and crowned with whipped topping.

title: Strawberry Vanilla Stuffed French Toast
description: An unbeatable flavor combination! Warm cinnamon raisin French toast is stuffed with sweet cream filling, then topped with sliced glazed strawberries, a drizzle of vanilla cream, a dusting of powdered sugar and cool and creamy whipped topping.

title: Philly Cheese Steak Stacker
description: This signature favorite is inspired by the city of Brotherly Love. It comes stacked with grilled Philly steak and onions, then topped with melted American cheese on a perfectly grilled roll.

title: Chicken Bacon Griller
description: A juicy, grilled chicken breast with melted Provolone cheese, fire-roasted tomato spread, fresh lettuce and bacon on a grilled bun. It's a griller that's sure to thrill.

title: Turkey & Bacon Club Sandwich
description: This club is stacked with roast turkey, crispy bacon, Cheddar cheese, fresh sliced tomatoes, lettuce and mayonnaise and served on a grilled roll.

title: Pot Roast Melt
description: A mouthwatering melt made with tender slow-cooked USDA Choice beef pot roast with caramelized onions in rich beef and mushroom gravy, topped with melted Swiss and American cheeses on grilled sourdough bread.
